name: 2024 the 6th International Conference on Robotics Systems and Automation Engineering
content: Publication: All accepted papers will be published into RSAE 2024 Conference Proceedings, which will be published in the International Conference Proceedings Series by ACM, which will be archived in ACM Digital Library, and indexed by EI Compendex, Scopus, and submitted to be reviewed by Thomson Reuters Conference Proceedings Citation Index (ISI Web of Science). The ISBN number assigned to RSAE 2024 is 979-8-4007-1786-4.
